newsArray.title: At home, Sanju Samson faces moment of reckoning ahead of World Cup
newsArray.description: Local hero Sanju Samson faces mounting pressure as his inconsistent batting form jeopardizes his T20 World Cup chances. Despite support from coaches, a lack of role clarity and recent subdued performances have left selectors with tough decisions. With limited opportunities remaining, Samson's career hangs in the balance as India weighs its options.

newsArray.title: ICC announces match officials for Men's T20 World Cup 2026 group stage
newsArray.description: Dubai [UAE], January 30 (ANI): The International Cricket Council (ICC) on Friday confirmed the appointments of match officials for the group stage of the Men's T20 World Cup 2026, which gets underway on February 7.A total of 24 on-field umpires and six match referees will oversee the opening phase, with officials for the Super Eight and knockout rounds to be announced later, according to the ICC website.T
